name: ABDL White Diaper
description: I created this model via Kohya and about 40 unique photos of women wearing all white diapers. It works best on SD1.5 and 1.4 models. I have tried it with realistic vision and it works OK with that too. Prompts lean hard towards women so you have to pretty much force the prompt to generate men. Faces will typically need inpainting as well to look half decent. I'm not sure if that is because of the base model I trained on or my training, but inpainting works well and I don't really care to look into cleaning that up. I didn't train this on any art so if does do art that's a happy coincidence. Since this took such little time to train, I may try to do another model using printed diapers to see if I can get reliable diaper patterns to generate. Leave some feedback.
